metadata.name: Jasper - America's Dog
metadata.description:
America's Dog Jasper

Personal Muse To: Dana Perino

I am just a Vizsla, and my story's often told

'Cause I'm an Ethereum NFT

And I'm really rather famous at just nine years old.

Interests: Mom hugs. Walks with Dad. Sticky sticks. Fishy fish. The beach. Grass. Hunting squirrels. Toy piles. Peekaboo. Sidecar rides. Festive pajamas. Naps. Sweet, peanut butter dreams. The Five FNC. Gutfeld-eating penguins.

Tongue-out Tuesdays and Weekends - they're for the dogs!

I'm Amercia's dog Jasper, and people think I'm cool.

When they see me in the sidecar, or jumping 15 ft into the swimming pool

Or on TV with Mommy I live my life in style

But I'm just a happy puppy making everybody smile.
